1. vs-code-agents
------------------------------------------------------------------------------

Source: https://github.com/groupzer0/vs-code-agents
Author: groupzer0
License: MIT

The following files in this project are derivative works adapted from
vs-code-agents:

  agents/pidex-analyst.md
  agents/pidex-architect.md
  agents/pidex-code-reviewer.md
  agents/pidex-critic.md
  agents/pidex-devops.md
  agents/pidex-implementer.md
  agents/pidex-pi.md
  agents/pidex-planner.md
  agents/pidex-qa.md
  agents/pidex-retrospective.md
  agents/pidex-roadmap.md
  agents/pidex-security.md
  agents/pidex-uat.md
  pidex-instructions.md (incorporates rules and conventions)

These files were ported from the vs-code-agents Markdown agent format to
Claude Code's native subagent format with the "pidex-" prefix. The pipeline
structure, agent contracts, document conventions, and ID inheritance rules
are derived from vs-code-agents.

